query:
DELETE FROM fotos_formando 
WHERE execucaoFormandoId IN (
  SELECT ef.id 
  FROM execucao_formando ef
  JOIN formandos f ON ef.formandoId = f.id
  WHERE f.nome LIKE '%Álvaro Pontual%'
)
